Installing Claude Desktop Application on Slingshot for MCP Demo

Pre-requisites:  Install Claude Desktop following these instructions with binary package:
https://github.com/aaddrick/claude-desktop-debian

1. On slingshot linux, Place the claude_desktop_config.json into ~/.config/Claude/.

2. Place the security_server.py into a new directory:
/home/sec598/tools/security-mcp-server/src

3. Place the requirements.txt into:
/home/sec598/tools/security-mcp-server

4. Note:  You might need to do a pip install

5. Replace your Virustotal API Key in claude_desktop_config.json
